markets.title: What will Dollar General say on their Q1 FY2025 earnings call?
markets.rules_primary: If Egg is said by any Dollar General representative during the earnings call (including the Q+A) for Q1 FY2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Audio of the earnings call will be used to resolve the market. The exact phrase/word, or a plural or possessive form of the phrase/word, must be used. Grammatical/tense inflections are otherwise not included. Hyphenated or compound words used with Egg will not be included.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
